Description
Actor
The Actor class is an abstract class representing an actor in the game.
ActorApplicationContextAware
The ActorApplicationContextAware class is a Spring component that implements the ApplicationContextAware interface.
ActorController
The ActorController class is a REST controller that handles HTTP requests related to actors in the application.
ActorDecoder
The ActorDecoder class implements the Jakarta WebSocket Decoder.Text interface to decode JSON messages into JsonNode objects.
ActorEncoder
The ActorEncoder class implements the Jakarta WebSocket Encoder.Text interface to encode objects into JSON strings.
ActorEndpoint
WebSocket endpoint for handling actor-related operations in a game.
ActorFactory
The ActorFactory class is responsible for creating instances of different types of actors.
ActorFactoryMethod
The ActorFactoryMethod interface defines a contract for creating actors in the game.
ActorService
The ActorService class provides services related to managing actors in the game.
CustomConfigurator
The CustomConfigurator class is a custom configuration class that extends ServerEndpointConfig.Configurator.
DiamondTreasure
The DiamondTreasure class represents a specific type of treasure in the game, namely a diamond treasure.
GoldTreasure
The GoldTreasure class represents a specific type of treasure in the game, namely a gold treasure.
MvcConfig
The MvcConfig class is a configuration class that implements the WebMvcConfigurer interface.
Police
The Police class represents a police actor in the game.
PoliceAndThieves
The main application class for the PoliceAndThieves application.
RedisConfig
The RedisConfig class is a configuration class for setting up the connection to a Redis data store.
SilverTreasure
The SilverTreasure class represents a specific type of treasure in the game, namely a silver treasure.
Table
The Table class represents the game board and handles the generation of the maze, as well as the management of actors and treasures within the game.
TableController
The TableController class is a REST controller that handles HTTP requests related to the game table and treasures.
TableService
The TableService class provides a service layer for interacting with the Table.
Thief
The Thief class represents a thief actor in the game.
TicketController
The TicketController class is a REST controller that handles HTTP requests related to tickets.
TicketRepository
The TicketRepository class is a repository component that manages tickets using Redis.
Treasure
The Treasure class represents a general treasure in the game.
TreasureFactory
The TreasureFactory class is responsible for creating instances of different types of treasures.
TreasureFactoryMethod
The TreasureFactoryMethod interface defines a contract for creating treasures.
WebSecurityConfig
The WebSecurityConfig class is a configuration class for setting up Spring Security in the application.
WebSocketConfig
The WebSocketConfig class is a configuration class for setting up WebSocket support in the application.
